room_title: Escape room "The Eyeland" by Know Way Out in Petoskey
room_description: You and the rest of the research team must follow in the footsteps of your mysteriously missing lead scientist, Dr. Scott Sorenson. His research surrounds the phenomenon of the Bermuda Triangle and the fact that, in recent years, its pull seems to be expanding. Will you prevail or will you, too, be sucked into the grips of the Bermuda Triangle like so many before you? You only have 60 minutes to find out.
